## Accessibility

### ARIA Attributes

```tsx
<button
  aria-label="Close dialog"
  aria-expanded={isOpen}
  onClick={handleClose}
>
  <XIcon />
</button>
```

### Keyboard Navigation

```tsx
<div
  role="button"
  tabIndex={0}
  onKeyDown={(e) => {
    if (e.key === 'Enter' || e.key === ' ') {
      handleClick();
    }
  }}
>
  Click me
</div>
```

---

## Prohibited Items

- ❌ Do not use `any` type
- ❌ Do not define components in render
- ❌ Do not directly modify props
- ❌ Do not use async directly in useEffect
- ❌ Do not ignore ESLint warnings
- ❌ Do not use inline styles (unless necessary)
